- Open the vault.
- Jesse:<i> Hold on, hold on.</i>

34:31.667 --> 34:33.667
In the corner now.

34:38.291 --> 34:39.834
I know you.

34:41.625 --> 34:43.291
<i>Where'd you fight?</i>

34:43.291 --> 34:45.542
- I didn't.
- You did.

34:45.542 --> 34:47.542
You fought for the Union,
didn't you?

34:47.542 --> 34:49.542
No.

34:49.542 --> 34:54.333
Let's open the vault,
be on our way.

34:54.333 --> 34:56.333
- You fought at Richmond.
- No, I didn't.

34:56.333 --> 34:58.583
- Don't you shake
your head at me.
- Jesse.

35:02.458 --> 35:04.667
You're the man who shot
Bill Anderson.

35:06.458 --> 35:08.542
Gardner:
<i>The Civil War</i>
<i>made Jesse James.</i>

35:08.542 --> 35:11.458
<i>He killed men,</i>
<i>he saw men killed.</i>

35:11.458 --> 35:16.709
Seeing death every day changes
the way you look at life.

35:16.709 --> 35:19.333
<i> Jesse mistook</i>
<i> the teller</i>

35:19.333 --> 35:22.625
<i> for the murderer</i>
<i> of his leader during</i>
<i> the Civil War.</i>

35:22.625 --> 35:24.834
I found you,
you son of a bitch.

35:27.500 --> 35:30.333
( shouts )

