God damn it, Jesse.
On the floor!

35:46.542 --> 35:48.375
Frank:
<i>Come on, Jesse,</i>
<i>we got to go.</i>

35:48.375 --> 35:49.792
<i>Come on, now!</i>
<i>Come on.</i>

